cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper deals with object detection using convolutional neural networks and radar data for autonomous vehicles. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also deals with robotics and autonomous systems, which falls under cs.RO (Robotics). The use of neural networks and machine learning algorithms also suggests that the paper could be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of automated methods for training data generation, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper also discusses the use of radar data, which could fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
